# Session [11] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Mesh Topology chist?  (what is the mesh topology?)
- Device ha chetor dar Mesh ba ham ertebat migiran?  (how does devices communicate to eachother?
- Broadcast Domain dar Mesh topology chetor kar mikonad? (how does broadcast work in mesh topology?)

## Flashback – Mesh Basics
- Dar Mesh → har device mitavanad be chand device digar vasl shavad  
- Traffic mitavanad az masir haye mokhtalef be destination beresad  
- Mesh 2 halt dard (Partial) = (full)

### Mesh Partial or Mesh full?
- furmull mohasebe | Wan conection<n-1 |  
- Mesh partial = age wan connection ma kkochak tar bashe ma darim az topology partial mesh estefade mikonim
- Mesh full = age wan ma bozorg tar ya mosavi bood ma darim az topology full mesh estefade mikonam

## Explanation

### Mesh Topology
- Har node (AP ya device) be chand node digar link darad  
- Age ye masir ghat beshe → traffic az masir digar miravad  
- Reliability bala ast, chon yek masir nist — chand raah vojood darad  
- Mashhoor dar wireless city networks, sensor networks, mehvarha-ye outdoor  

### Broadcast Domain
- Dar Mesh topology → hame node ha ke be ham link daran **dar yek broadcast domain hastand**  
- Broadcast az ye node → tamame node haye link shode migiran  
- Be hodood-e physical link ha bastegi darad  

